The Thursday Murder Club by @misterosman & featuring Bearlock Holmes from London! 
üìö 
Thank you @betterreadingau for the advance copy in exchange for a review!
üìö 
‚ÄúWe each of us understand we‚Äôre in a gang and we understand we are in the middle of something unusual. We understand also, I think, that we are doing something illegal, but we are past the age of caring. Perhaps we are raging against the dying of the light, but that is poetry, not life.‚Äù
üìö 
In Kent, in a quaint retirement village called Coopers Chase, four elderly residents meet up every Thursday to solve cold cases as a way to keep busy. That is until a real life murder occurs on their doorstep. You generally wouldn‚Äôt classify a murder mystery as fun, but this is exactly what this book is. Elizabeth, Ron, Ibrahim and Joyce come from totally different walks of life, but together they make an entertaining and efficient quartet, using their life skills and devilish charm and wit to gather the information they need to solve the case, even cheekily bargaining with police officers DCI Chris Hudson and PC Donna De Freitas. 
üìö 
Just when you think you have the murder solved, the book propels you in a whole new direction, opening up new storylines and reveals without becoming too complicated. 
üìö 
While this book is entertaining and light, there is also a slight melancholy side to it, touching on the love, loss, regret and the very real fear and realization that Elizabeth, Ron, Ibrahim and Joyce feel at almost being at the end of their road. 
üìö 
Steeped in classic British humour, this is one book that you want to settle down with and pair with a cuppa! I‚Äôm so looking forward to Book 2!";}i:30;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:31;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:2;}i:32;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvOwj-gBYX";}i:33;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:250:"https://scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/118710894_1266245903707256_1163407400050037436_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_ohc=QiiOLFUk2LoAX-YXZrL&oh=7429faa865186eedb21cf8c9eb97cbec&oe=5F7E1DE4";}i:34;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:35;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:39904388912;}i:36;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:37;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:38;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:39;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391194388106933404";}i:40;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvOqB8BXSc";}i:41;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599272605;}i:42;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:241:"...

